{"tid":132106,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【差佬晒馬】藍絲要立辱警罪 葉劉潑冷水：普通法冇以言入罪","createTime":"2017-02-23T14:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T18:13:22.000Z","uid":48093,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a383378b8e6a4a1c10d563cf9d685e932386638","tid":132106,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170223/large/1487858725_cfe9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170223%2Flarge%2F1487858725_cfe9.jpg&h=f8490a01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少警粉和撐警的建制派人士借7警案，再提設立「辱警罪」，不過同屬建制派的保安局前局長葉劉淑儀則唱反調，認為現時已有法例針對傷害公職人員、阻差辦公等，若要為「辱警罪」立法，將非常困難。<br />\n<br />\n她解釋，「喺普通法入面，係冇以言入罪」，故「辱警罪」難草擬成功，即使立法後，亦難檢控成功。她認為政府要多教育社會，提倡公職人員和市民也要文明一些，「唔好咁粗暴」。"},{"pid":"76a2faffce7a47adbaa82b0211febf9d8ee226a9","tid":132106,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:59:27.000Z","msg":"但係23條有冇？"},{"pid":"4b446b0e54a0b5720ffd9322bc18a2b0c3801eba","tid":132106,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:01:37.000Z","msg":"又唔見台上當場講"},{"pid":"4c521a519501e701f4c5dd67d3ee9a508f5810e3","tid":132106,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n背棄劏房户之約，改邪歸正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb347f12d5ed37f93b4b72d8951fc87233570d34","tid":132106,"uid":84265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:31:51.000Z","msg":"咁廿三條呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4f32ce8f522b2aa3715dd638b6aa681f41b9e6","tid":132106,"uid":6041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:32:52.000Z","msg":"葉劉bb 係咪病左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n